history.content:
With 197 open seats and you being on position 200, I'd say you have a pretty good chance of getting into the class.

Those 200 seats are blocked from enrollment until TA hiring is completed. So once they open up, you are likely to get in right away..

As an undeclared freshmen who met the prerequisites, how likely would I enroll in CS C100 if I am placed 200 on the waitlist? Also, I am curious about who are those available seats reserved for. Any advice is greatly appreciated.
